        <p>

                                                Over 11 billion paper receipts are printed in the UK each year, <br> on thermal receipt paper that cannot be recycled. <br><br>


        <p>Here's our solution</p>


            <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/P1QS-myvKb4?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe><br><br><br>
            
        
        <p>We are currently working with stores to bring this service to you as soon as possible.<br><br>

Until then, you can download our app on iOS and Android, which lets you to turn paper receipts into digital ones and use them in store.</p>
        
                <a class="apple" href="https://geo.itunes.apple.com/gb/app/nujjreceipts/id1057023005?mt=8" style="display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;background:url(http://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/images/badges/en-us/badge_appstore-lrg.svg) no-repeat; background-size: 35vw 10vw; width:35vw;height:10vw;"></a><br>

